summary: An Ordinance authorizing and directing the Mayor and City Comptroller of the City of Seattle to make, execute and deliver unto Eugene A. Childe a deed to the East nineteen (19) feet of Lot Five (5), Block Forty-seven (47), Kilbourne's Supplemental of Lake Union Addition to the City of Seattle, upon payment by said Childe of all general taxes and local assessments of whatsoever character due and owing upon said property.
